These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, water
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, red, lilac
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, soccer
House: futuristic, victorian, ranch-style
 1. the futuristic house and the person who likes red have different parity positions##9
 2. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 3. the futuristic house is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the person who likes turquise and the person drinking hot-chocolate have different parity positions##9
 6. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking water##1
 7. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 8. the victorian house is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person who likes red and the person drinking water have different parity positions##9
10. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | fanta | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Music-Genre   | turquise       | red   | lilac   |
| Nationality   | volleyball    | surfing | soccer  |
| Transport     | ranch-style   | victorian       | futuristic |

