.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, blues, house
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, sprite
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, ferret
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, pall-mall, bluemaster
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the fan house##5
2. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the fan classical##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
4. the owner of the fish and the fan blues have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking soy-milk and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
6. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
8. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | house  | classical         | blues |
| Hobby         | soy-milk | sprite | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | guinea-pig     | ferret       | fish     |
| Transport     | davidoff       | pall-mall          | bluemaster    |

