3. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
5. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
8. the person who growsamaryllis and the person playing domino have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | amaryllis | orchid | azalea |
