City: venice, miami, berlin
1. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
2. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
3. the person who likes red and the person who's birthday is in october have different parity positions##9
4. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
5. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
7. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
8. the person who likes ivory is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |       3       |
| Job           | september    | october | march |
| Movie-Genre   | red | ivory       | light-blue     |
| Pet           | watermelon        | potato      | radish          |
| Transport     | miami        | berlin         | venice     |

