5. the person traveling to prague and the ranch-style house have the same parity positions##9
6. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
7. the fan folk is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
8. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
9. the person playing poker is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
